{"tid":2077367,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英微信被河蟹 重登聲明反駁中共謬論","createTime":"2020-06-24T08:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T09:17:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eadfd06067d21d41ad626c4e305ac1abbf5fbd0e","tid":2077367,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/RJIUKTCTTDI5R2W7TQRIE6AXBY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FRJIUKTCTTDI5R2W7TQRIE6AXBY%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=f58f8dcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FRJIUKTCTTDI5R2W7TQRIE6AXBY%2F&h=0428c25b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/RJIUKTCTTDI5R2W7TQRIE6AXBY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英微信被河蟹 重登聲明反駁中共謬論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FA765V7DRQUY7AFUV3XIQKGAEI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFA765V7DRQUY7AFUV3XIQKGAEI.gif&h=b1a25b8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英外相藍韜文在Twitter指聲明遭微信審查表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國駐華使館上周在微信公眾號發佈《關於香港問題的更正說明》一文，逐點反駁中方近期針對英國圍繞香港議題的言論，但文章迅速被刪。英政府不甘打壓，昨於其官網重新上載同一聲明，重申《中英聯合聲明》是國際公約，中方有責任履行承諾；官媒報道所指的290萬港人支持國安法，是來自中聯辦操控的問卷。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刑事案法官絕非特首指派<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學者稱中方刪文章得不償失<br />\n<br />\n聲明針對官媒八篇報道逐一反駁，包括英國對港立場，如英國支持港獨、外國干涉引起香港抗議活動、英方不願意譴責香港的暴力行為等。英政府重申明確承認在一國兩制的框架下香港是中國的一部份，而英方支持和平示威的權利，強調暴力示威和毀壞公物是不能接受的。<br />\n<br />\n中方言論提及《中英聯合聲明》是歷史文件，不具備現實意義。。。。防等事項，其享有的權利和自由50年不變。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法是另一大火頭，中方稱港版國安法的通過是依。。。。並引用《明報》調查反駁，64%的港人反對港版國安法。<br />\n<br />\n英國駐華使館在微信上的文章，被指涉嫌違反相關法律及政策。。。。一，有權表達英方的顧慮，對聲明遭審查表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n香港智明研究所研究總監許楨分析，英國奉行「外交無小事」，所有的外國行徑必先經過深思熟慮及沙盤推演，有預計方案。他指英方聲明內容簡單、易明及鮮明，兩國有不同看法是正常，「但係咪要嚴重到刪咗佢呢？點解唔用中文反駁呢？」<br />\n<br />\n許楨認為刪除聲明只會削弱內地人的知情權，雖然英方未必。。。。大，中方此舉可說是得不償失。<br />\n<br />\n國際關係學者沈旭暉稱，外交慣例不能刪除其他國家的微信聲明，相信英方是以更正式的方式發表聲明，作為一種不滿宣示。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4VWUS355RGG76T5OX2FZCQW7BM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4VWUS355RGG76T5OX2FZCQW7BM.gif&h=d806ca0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36a3733317a097125c92c640593492b5eca1123d","tid":2077367,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmbxE55hyYzQ&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPmlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=707dbced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mbxE55hyYzQ</a>"},{"pid":"d44337f57928f2852cbff309285efea581f342c5","tid":2077367,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T08:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2784ce8b325dda142a9612deab3f1d26bdb622a6","tid":2077367,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"終於日出？"},{"pid":"e0434930ec8c913c08c8ee6c1f6edb77a9b26bf4","tid":2077367,"uid":269137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"the People's Republic of Censorship<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}